p.k: Granville is having a cut price sale but only on old stock, not the boiled ham! Meanwhile, there's an air of romance around as Mrs. Featherstone takes a shine to a new resident, Mr. Newbold. United Kingdom (2015). Cast: David Jason, Lynda Baron, James Baxter, Stephanie Cole, Maggie Ollerenshaw, Brigit Forsyth, Johnny Vegas, Kulvinder Ghir, Nina Wadia, Tim Healy. Director: Dewi Humphreys.
